# AI Agent Rules

## Project Structure
- This project follows a Nuxt 3 structure.
- Agent Skills and Workflows are located in `.agent/`.

## Key Skills
- **Clone Section**: See `.agent/clone-section/SKILL.md`.
- **Agent Skills**: See `.agent/agent-skills/SKILL.md`.

## Coding Standards
- Use Vue 3 Composition API with `<script setup>`.
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling.
